{"tid":258960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"樓市已到頂峰","createTime":"2017-05-26T14:13:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-28T04:30:19.000Z","uid":13663,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aac3a095fd49949c2daa4c6e19e11993c729041a","tid":258960,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T14:13:48.000Z","msg":"我話既<br />\n一年後可以拎出黎binc<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f415847bfa290edb0207ca2d7028cf3d04e81267","tid":258960,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T15:19:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7557d22ecc8e4c6971e4dc7fcf219cc702fa9ec0","tid":258960,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T15:44:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61f5e5802a546875986ab029e573699d7dbe85a0","tid":258960,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T15:45:40.000Z","msg":"留名，btw點都拎啲野出嚟賭呀"},{"pid":"7bc344d781c4b514e37c287195b3d5956f68b38d","tid":258960,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T15:54:49.000Z","msg":"施永青唔係咁講喎"},{"pid":"a24a60b805d0f13c9f7e4763bf444cd003db7442","tid":258960,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T16:03:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65a783a784706fb8091128979bd098a4b71527aa","tid":258960,"uid":64047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T16:05:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我話既<br />\n一年後可以拎出黎binc<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一個鐘後都無人回啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccfeab2cef6d25871e0829571a86d8f923a21605","tid":258960,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T16:12:40.000Z","msg":"【97vs17樓市】施永青：樓市唔會咁快爆煲！ 原因有三個&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170526/large/1495790031_41d1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170526%2Flarge%2F1495790031_41d1.jpg&h=84fcc7e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【新增影片】<br />\n長實（1113）荃灣海之戀今日首輪賣樓，現場萬人空卷，買家條隊由紅磡置富都會排到入火車站，狂搶樓情況似足97賣樓。中原集團創辦人施永青表示，多方面睇又未必同97年情況一樣，暫時睇唔到樓市好快會爆煲。<br />\n<br />\n樓價高企，樓市氣氛依然熾熱，情況同97相似，泡沫即將爆破？施永青認為，「 係咪咁旺就好多因素影響，暫時就睇唔到佢好快會爆煲囉 」，一般地產泡沫爆煲有三種因素影響：過度建設、過度借貸以及（樓價）過度上升。他解釋，首先香港冇過度建設，反而係唔夠建設；亦冇過度借貸，「香港有六成幾小業主供甩樓，你供甩樓就好少話變負資產呀，被銀行逼倉呀，呢啲情況97就多，依家香港人唔算投資好勇，所以就過度借貸爆煲機會少啲。」最後雖然樓價對用家嚟講係過度上升，但對投資者嚟講仲有能力負擔。<br />\n<br />\n施永青指，現時樓市暢旺係因為社會上積累好多資金，雖然樓價同用家購買力脫節，好多人都買唔起，跌一兩成都有排未跌到佢地買得起嘅程度，但有能力嘅人依然仲係買緊。對於政府出招抑壓樓市，他認為，「政府依家出嘅招，係企圖增加入市難度呀嘛，但呢個有時益咗有錢個批」，依家出嚟買樓嘅人以前未用過私人名買啫，但唔首次置業，大把樓住。"},{"pid":"5387d80c3eb2a92979a97f9f35e4b2f70c440997","tid":258960,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T17:00:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18f27e8d88971262526c0e97e6cf371acbcbfe19","tid":258960,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T17:25:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd4a506e9fe291430c81137647c34c46a8a8f4d0","tid":258960,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T17:29:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e44607441b7f09d96545d31f6a7ecd30df4a5d92","tid":258960,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T17:39:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9a366fdb37e2d25fcf471bd0878a9b9a95b3db0","tid":258960,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:19:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4a5bb477d10a3baddb362a5049d8a737dd6031a","tid":258960,"uid":31208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:22:39.000Z","msg":"2009: 樓市已到頂峰<br />\n2010: 樓市已到頂峰<br />\n⋯⋯⋯⋯<br />\n2007: 樓市已到頂峰<br />\n<br />\n蘋果已死"},{"pid":"4839c1f1c9ab7e1509aceb33bb99640057c306bd","tid":258960,"uid":79442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:29:50.000Z","msg":"但係唔會暴跌，咁最後就會走平"},{"pid":"6d37a48d670fc8c16511af22a221303c3a49714b","tid":258960,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T05:08:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5bceff9d59a7fa83c980fb093edf193a0ae2dc9","tid":258960,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T05:31:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"714853a74a4e944ee66337fd9744ccbe704a4b32","tid":258960,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T07:20:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4f7e274d6cdbc6f3dc4b879cc4abbffbf0d94a8","tid":258960,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T04:30:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}